Method.КакXDTO.Param.НаборСхемXML.Description=An XML schema set used for validation of the document being read.\nIf a schema set is specified but not validated and XML document validation is enabled, the schema set is validated.\n See details of the method XMLReader.OpenStream in the Syntax Assistant
Method.КакXDTO.Param.ПараметрыЧтенияXML.Description=Parameters for reading XML data\n See details of the method XMLReader.OpenStream in the Syntax Assistant
Method.КакXDTO.Return.Description=Return value can have any type that supports serialization to XDTO.
