Method.НовыеПараметры.Return.МаксимальноеВремяПовторов.Description=maximum total time (in seconds) for sending the request including retries.\nDefault value\: 600.
Method.НовыеПараметры.Return.МаксимальноеКоличествоПовторов.Description=number of connection/request send retries.\nAn exponentially growing delay is applied between retries.\nBut if the status code is one of 413, 429, 503\nand the response has a Retry-After header,\nthe delay is derived from this header's value\nDefault value\: 0 - retries are not performed.
